You will now be asked to rate yourself under various category headings.  Please take your time and answer honestly.  This will enable you to receive valid and constructive feedback for your own personal development.
 
Please select one answer for each statement.

You will now be asked to rate the employee under various category headings.  Please take your time and answer honestly.  This will enable the employee to receive valid and constructive feedback for their own personal development.
 
Please select one answer for each statement.

360 Degree Feedback Survey
 
The purpose of this survey is to evaluate your overall performance with regards to the organizations' goals and values.
This survey will be issued to your chosen co-workers, direct reports, managers and senior managers (up to 12 people).
The results will be issued to you via email and will be anonymous (within 6 weeks).  You will be able to see how all your raters scored you against how you scored yourself.
The feedback should be discussed with your direct manager at your next performance review.
 
Please note that this evaluation will be included in your overall performance management process and other performance processes you are involved with, will remain.
 
Each grouping of performance indicators will be rated using the following scale:
  • Outstanding/Role Model - exceeds beyond expectations
  • Capable and Effective - good performance and demonstrates full competence
  • Could benefit from Development - getting by, but should consider ways of making improvements in order to meet the standard
  • Needs significant Improvement - a performance shortfall.  This should be a top priority for development action and discussion with direct manager/supervisor.

Please request or attend a 360 degree feedback consulatation before evaluating your's or anyone else's performance.
 
Thank you
